[genericglass Collins] Serving Glass: Collins With Ice

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
1 1/2 oz [genericingredient Gin] Beefeater Gin
1/2 oz [genericingredient Apricot Brandy] Hiram Walker Apricot Brandy
1/2 oz [genericingredient Anisette] Hiram Walker Anisette
1/2 oz [genericingredient Lemon Juice] Lemon Juice
Shake and Strain
Fill Club Soda
Garnish: Lemon Slice

